Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.57,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,derp,Back then, mom was still alive, and dad was kind. Back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Say, Kyou-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,I have a favor to ask of you.{long}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:38.40,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Back then, I made a promise to mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A very important promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan! Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if your fever is gone yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My temperature is the same as yours, so that means it's gone!{FORESHADOWING}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go deliver the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, don't go out there.{you can't}
Comment: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you went on your newspaper run during rainy days, your cold got even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! It's all about mind over matter!{病は気から 【やまいはきから】 (exp) sickness and health start with the mind}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, you should really stay in bed!{blarg}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother went to heaven the year she gave birth to Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our father disappeared after accumulating gambling debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus, we were abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a 40-year-old, one-room, dilapidated apartment with no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:57.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, the rice porridge is done!{粥 【かゆ】 (n) thin rice porridge; watery cooked rice; rice gruel;}
Comment: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
