Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.57,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,No, no! I have to hurry up and get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:12.49,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I can't continue making Asu worry like this.
