Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that was the idea, but it seems like maybe it wasn't such a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a hospital, you know! They'll throw us out!{CREATIVE FUCKING LIBERTIES OKAY}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'd love to hear Ichinokura-san's song.{idk anymore. bleh}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I feel like it'd help me get better.{fuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll sing because you said so, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.61,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan is late, huh?{on another note, WHY DOESN'T THIS GUY LEARN A NEW FUCKING SONG OH WELL AT LEAST THAT SAVES ME THE AGONY OF FIXING THE HORRIBLY TRANSLATED LYRICS OF AN ALL NEW MASTERPIECE}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dandelions...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,These are Mom's favorite flowers!{hm, rather than sepia, maybe I should add some kind of bloom or something}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,I'll take some to Mom in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:35.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Mom always smiles when she sees dandelions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,That's why, if I bring them to her, she'll get better again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:47.68,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Back then, I would gather flowers day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Mom! Mom! I brought you some more flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was nothing I could do.{probably could be better linked to the current situation}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Kyou, you brought me some dandelions again, didn't you?{DANDELIONS IN A VASE, YOU SEE FLOWERS IN THESE WEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEDS}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I promised, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Thank you.{k so would it be weird to make her mom's speech all bloom-y >__>}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Looking at the dandelions you've brought me always helps me forget about my sickness.{FUCK. FUCK. FUCK.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom's smile... She looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Hey, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Why do you smile whenever you see dandelions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:16:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,You see, it's because the dandelions look so happy and carefree to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,They look happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,That's why they remind me of you, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Just like the dandelions, you always seem to be smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,That's why I smile whenever I see dandelions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Mom wasn't smiling because she was looking at the dandelions...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was smiling because she saw my smile.{"face" is a more accurate translation but I really like this phrasing better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, I never smiled for Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:02.88,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:06.64,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, don’t try to take anybody else’s place.{lifted right out of episode 4, 17:54}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu.{I'm like 90% sure they just forgot to animate her mouth. I think that explains why it magically disappeared.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:14.68,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,You’re my older sister. Stay that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:19.35,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Okay, I will. I'll be right here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.99,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:27.58,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I... What the heck was I doing? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thing that only I can do for Asu. The most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Onee-chan is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope she hasn't tired herself out worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:06.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to handle the hospital fees, too. Maybe I'm just being an annoyance to her.{for fuck's sake could these people be any more self-deprecating}
Comment: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:33.00,generic sign style,,0,0,0,,Good night, Asu! Get well soon!{jesus fuck she's probably paying more for the batteries them niggerlights is using than the hospital bill will cost.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Onee-chanQ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.33,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:46.22,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan's smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks just like a dandelion!{okay, I lost it. I just... }
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on being discharged, Asu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure to take it easy for a while, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all you've done.{WHY DO YOU NEED TO THANK THEM, YOU'RE FUCKING PAYING THEM FOR IT :V}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Onee-chan, there's a place I'd like to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't push yourself too much, okay?{tough it out like that anymore}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, at first, your cold was far worse than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so worried about you that I forgot to take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right here, Mom asked me to do something.
Comment: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a long time ago, but this is where I heard it.{um wait...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,I'm your big sister! Do you understand me?{JESUS CHRIST HOW MANY TIMES WILL THEY REPEAT THIS}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with Mom's voice.{these are fragments. DO I LOOK LIKE I GIVE A FUCK}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,I ask you, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Protect... Your big sister.{idk this is probably supposed to be broken english anyway but fuck that shitniggersidon'tgiveafucksofuckthatshityoufuckingfaggots}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your big sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please protect her, she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Asu, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't remember this{her} at all, but I get the feeling that that was what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I've promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'll protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will protect Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:43.89,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Mother, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:47.77,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,We're keeping our promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a 40-year-old, one-room, dilapidated apartment with no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Onee-chan, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, they're in full bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:17.07,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,We're very happy together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, this is bad! Really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.02,0:21:24.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sakura-viewing has come inside!{has come to us}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,